*Assessment*

As part of inspecting the health of the [cloud in the Eucalyptus Administration Guide|http://www.eucalyptus.com/docs/eucalyptus/3.3/admin-guide/inspect_health.html], users are told to check the following URL:
{code}
http://CLCIPADDRESS:8773/services/Heartbeat
{code}

Unfortunately, the status doesn't match the output of euca-describe-services and/or euca-describe-components.

*Signs*

